---
// "公告"页面 (announcements.astro)
import Layout from '../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';
---
<Layout title="开篇 · 心声">
    <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-8">
            “我的人生，是一场白雪茫茫的黑夜...”
        </p>

        <div class="audio-player-container max-w-lg mx-auto bg-gray-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-2">序章</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Athen Drakmvese</p>
            <audio controls class="w-full" preload="auto">
                <source src="/prologue.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
                您的浏览器不支持音频播放。
            </audio>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-gray-600">
            <p>如果你也碰巧走进了这里，不必急着寻找出路。</p>
            <p>可以坐下，一起看看这片黑夜里的雪。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
<style>
    audio { border-radius: 50px; }
</style>